{"tid":1008179,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洪水橋輕鐵撞旅遊巴 至少20人受傷","createTime":"2019-02-04T09:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T23:11:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1f34863c4af66af78a83a9fb7f5fd5640882f6e2","tid":1008179,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190204/large/1549271899_5b63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190204%2Flarge%2F1549271899_5b63.jpg&h=451f580a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190204/large/1549272529_5e52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190204%2Flarge%2F1549272529_5e52.jpg&h=c81a823b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洪水橋發生輕鐵與旅遊巴相撞意外，下午5時許，現場為亦園路青山公路交界，一部旅遊巴與輕鐵相撞，現場消息稱，至少20人受傷。消防接報後，派出10部救護車前往現場協助處理傷者。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，輕鐵鍾屋村站附近的服務受阻，呼籲乘客考慮使用其他交通工具。運輸署指青山公路洪水橋段往元朗方向近亦園路的部份行車線現已封閉。駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車，現時交通繁忙。<br />\n<br />\n受事件影響，輕鐵路綫改道如下：<br />\n<br />\n610綫，614綫，615綫及751綫改道，將不停藍地站至洪水橋站。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵已安排免費接駁巴士，行走來往兆康至元朗，以及來往兆康至天水圍接載受影響車站的乘客。<br />\n<br />\n意外現場的青山公路與亦園路交界曾發生多宗同類意外，2011年8月9日，41歲姓何婦人駕駛一部七人車沿青山公路左轉入亦園路時，一列開往元朗的615號線輕鐵列車駛至，猛撞向七人車左邊車身，並將車推前10多米。被攔腰猛撞的七人車橫亘路軌上，何被困車廂，頭部受重創，消防到場撬開車門將何婦救出，送院後證實不治。2010年1月曾發生車禍，一部保時捷四驅車與一部輕鐵列車相撞，四驅車嚴重損毀，一名女乘客受傷。<br />\n<br />\n據運輸署資料，青山公路與亦園路交界並非交通黑點，現場設有交通燈號及清晰道路標誌，指示輕鐵及其他車輛使用該路口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190204/59223866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F59223866&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ25pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=a6ed3d45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F59223866&h=f67eca55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190204/59223866</a>"},{"pid":"b56e88017d6ec039ba4f9955867dd46f4f3af2a5","tid":1008179,"uid":228963,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0981cbbc6643cce5438e873641be8f46e4498291","tid":1008179,"uid":13370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"旅遊巴車頭好似寫住「海關」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1d4639a7e881407a72d8e8387b99ebdd354feb","tid":1008179,"uid":38456,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/8/81/逆緣.jpg/250px-逆緣.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F8%2F81%2F%E9%80%86%E7%B7%A3.jpg%2F250px-%E9%80%86%E7%B7%A3.jpg&h=45c24187&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de8544e05402acfe1d93f105a91187817d58d328","tid":1008179,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0981cbbc6643cce5438e873641be8f46e4498291","tid":1008179,"uid":13370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"旅遊巴車頭好似寫住「海關」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"因為旅遊巴有份接送政府機構員工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f2137746059d5185d3591541d3e51de6c3260d","tid":1008179,"uid":182041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a7fa642eaa8b87646a94bd19faa4ef0a7aae43","tid":1008179,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:23:40.000Z","msg":"又係撞支那車"},{"pid":"e0b097ca3afa513d978d3ca30e167148c01bea84","tid":1008179,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re